{%- comment -%}
  Section: C Science Proof Grid
  Description: Two-column science/proof section with a full-bleed background image, editorial content panel, and block-based metrics card.
  sl-id: sl-section-science-proof-grid-v1
  Figma: https://www.figma.com/design/f1AWMl23NcBW13s8SML1B5/BKL?node-id=5789-10720&m=dev
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign sl_id = 'sl-section-science-proof-grid-v1'
  assign section_anchor_id = section.settings.sl_anchor_id | default: section.id
-%}

{%- capture clinical_trials_drawer_body_default -%}
  <p>Only a small percentage of dietary supplements are tested in gold-standard human clinical trials.</p>
  <p>Berkeley Life® Nitric Oxide Support has been evaluated in double-blind, placebo-controlled research demonstrating its ability to increase nitric oxide bioavailability in humans.</p>
  <p>The dietary nitrate ingredients used in our formulation are supported by a growing body of peer-reviewed clinical research validating improvements in vascular function, endothelial health, and blood pressure regulation.</p>
  <h3>The Impact of Clinical Proof</h3>
  <p>Double-blind, placebo-controlled trials (DBPCTs) are considered the gold standard in scientific research because they help ensure:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Bias elimination</li>
    <li>Control for placebo effect</li>
    <li>Validated efficacy</li>
    <li>Safety and tolerability assessment</li>
  </ul>
  <p>By studying the full nitrate formulation as it is consumed, Berkeley Life® ensures the product is evaluated for real-world effectiveness and safety - not just theoretical ingredient benefits.</p>
  <h3>Nitric Oxide Production</h3>
  <p>Berkeley Life® is formulated to increase nitric oxide through the dietary nitrate → nitrite → nitric oxide pathway.</p>
  <p>Unlike L-arginine-based supplements, this pathway remains active even when endothelial nitric oxide synthase (eNOS) declines with age.</p>
  <h3>Clinical Trial Results</h3>
  <p>In a double-blind, placebo-controlled study, participants taking Berkeley Life® demonstrated significant increases in salivary nitrite and plasma nitrite compared to placebo. Test strip readings correlated with laboratory measurements, confirming improved nitric oxide bioavailability.</p>
  <h3>Vascular &amp; Endothelial Health</h3>
  <p>Nitric oxide is essential for healthy blood vessel function. It supports vasodilation, circulation, and endothelial integrity - all of which naturally decline with age.</p>
  <h3>Clinical Trial Results</h3>
  <p>In clinical research evaluating dietary nitrate supplementation over 12 weeks, participants showed improvements in endothelial function and reductions in carotid artery stiffness, a recognized marker of cardiovascular risk. These findings support the role of nitrate-based nitric oxide in maintaining vascular flexibility and heart health.</p>
  <h3>Blood Pressure Support</h3>
  <p>Nitric oxide helps relax and widen blood vessels, supporting healthy blood pressure regulation.</p>
  <h3>Clinical Trial Results</h3>
  <p>Clinical studies of dietary nitrates have demonstrated improvements in systolic blood pressure and vascular responsiveness compared to placebo, particularly with consistent daily use over 8-12 weeks.</p>
  <h3>Energy &amp; Oxygen Efficiency</h3>
  <p>Nitric oxide plays a critical role in oxygen delivery and mitochondrial signaling. Healthy nitric oxide levels support efficient energy production and muscle performance.</p>
  <h3>Clinical Research Findings</h3>
  <p>Research on dietary nitrates has shown improvements in oxygen utilization and exercise efficiency, including reduced oxygen cost during physical activity.</p>
  <h3>Aging &amp; Nitric Oxide Decline</h3>
  <p>Nitric oxide production naturally declines with age due to oxidative stress, hormonal shifts, and reduced enzyme activity.</p>
  <p>Berkeley Life® provides a nitrate-based pathway that supports nitric oxide production independently of age-related enzymatic decline, offering measurable vascular support as the body's natural production decreases.</p>
{%- endcapture -%}

<section
  id="{{ section_anchor_id }}"
  class="c-science-proof-grid"
  data-section-id="{{ section.id }}"
  data-sl-id="{{ sl_id }}"
  data-section-type="c-science-proof-grid"
>
  <div class="c-science-proof-grid__bg" aria-hidden="true">
    {%- if section.settings.background_image != blank -%}
      {{
        section.settings.background_image
        | image_url: width: 2400
        | image_tag:
          class: 'c-science-proof-grid__bg-image',
          loading: 'lazy',
          widths: '750, 1100, 1500, 2000, 2400',
          alt: section.settings.background_image_alt | escape
      }}
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>

  <div class="c-science-proof-grid__overlay"></div>

  <div class="c-science-proof-grid__container container-sl">
    <div class="c-science-proof-grid__intro">
      {%- if section.settings.subheading != blank -%}
        <p class="c-science-proof-grid__subheading">{{ section.settings.subheading }}</p>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if section.settings.heading != blank -%}
        <h2 class="c-science-proof-grid__heading">{{ section.settings.heading }}</h2>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if section.settings.description != blank -%}
        <div class="c-science-proof-grid__description rte">
          {{ section.settings.description }}
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if section.settings.action_link_label != blank -%}
        {%- if section.settings.action_link_opens_modal -%}
          {%- liquid
            assign action_drawer_body = section.settings.action_drawer_body
            if action_drawer_body == blank
              assign action_drawer_body = clinical_trials_drawer_body_default
            endif
          -%}
          <div class="c-science-proof-grid__drawer-wrap">
            {%- render 'clinical-drawer',
              drawer_id: 'science-proof-grid-clinical-drawer-' | append: section.id,
              button_text: section.settings.action_link_label,
              button_style: 'default',
              drawer_title: section.settings.action_drawer_title,
              drawer_body: action_drawer_body,
              bg_color: section.settings.action_drawer_bg_color,
              text_color: section.settings.action_drawer_text_color
            -%}
          </div>
        {%- else -%}
          <a
            class="c-science-proof-grid__action-link"
            {% if section.settings.action_link_url != blank %}
              href="{{ section.settings.action_link_url }}"
            {% else %}
              role="link"
              aria-disabled="true"
            {% endif %}
          >
            <span>{{ section.settings.action_link_label }}</span>
            <svg class="c-science-proof-grid__action-icon" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
              <path d="M3 8H13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
              <path d="M9.5 4.5L13 8L9.5 11.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>

    <div class="c-science-proof-grid__metrics">
      {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
        <article class="c-science-proof-grid__metric" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
          <div class="c-science-proof-grid__metric-header">
            {%- if block.settings.title != blank -%}
              <h3 class="c-science-proof-grid__metric-title">{{ block.settings.title }}</h3>
            {%- endif -%}

            <div class="c-science-proof-grid__metric-icon-wrap">
              {%- if block.settings.icon != blank -%}
                {{
                  block.settings.icon
                  | image_url: width: 96
                  | image_tag:
                    class: 'c-science-proof-grid__metric-icon',
                    loading: 'lazy',
                    widths: '48, 72, 96',
                    alt: block.settings.icon_alt | escape
                }}
              {%- else -%}
                <span class="c-science-proof-grid__metric-icon-placeholder" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              {%- endif -%}
            </div>
          </div>

          {%- if block.settings.description != blank -%}
            <p class="c-science-proof-grid__metric-description">{{ block.settings.description }}</p>
          {%- endif -%}

          {%- if block.settings.value != blank -%}
            <p class="c-science-proof-grid__metric-value">{{ block.settings.value }}</p>
          {%- endif -%}

          {%- if block.settings.value_caption != blank -%}
            <p class="c-science-proof-grid__metric-caption">{{ block.settings.value_caption }}</p>
          {%- endif -%}
        </article>
      {%- endfor -%}

      {%- if section.settings.cta_text != blank -%}
        <div class="c-science-proof-grid__cta">
          <a href="{{ section.settings.cta_link }}" class="c-science-proof-grid__cta-button">
            {{ section.settings.cta_text }}
          </a>
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% style %}
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid {
    --c-science-proof-grid-text: {{ section.settings.text_color }};
    --c-science-proof-grid-accent: {{ section.settings.accent_color }};
    --c-science-proof-grid-cyan: {{ section.settings.value_color }};
    --c-science-proof-grid-intro-bg: {{ section.settings.intro_background_color }};
    --c-science-proof-grid-metrics-bg: {{ section.settings.metrics_background_color }};
    --c-science-proof-grid-metrics-border: {{ section.settings.metrics_border_color }};
    --c-science-proof-grid-overlay: {{ section.settings.background_overlay_color }};
    --c-science-proof-grid-caption: {{ section.settings.caption_color }};
    --c-science-proof-grid-max: 1280px;
    color: var(--c-science-proof-grid-text);
    display: block;
    isolation: isolate;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__bg,
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__overlay {
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    position: absolute;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__bg-image {
    display: block;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    width: 100%;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__overlay {
    background: var(--c-science-proof-grid-overlay);
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__container {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    display: grid;
    gap: 24px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: var(--c-science-proof-grid-max);
    padding-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom_mobile }}px;
    padding-top: {{ section.settings.padding_top_mobile }}px;
    padding-left: 20px;
    padding-right: 20px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__intro,
  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__metrics {
    border-radius: 24px;
    min-width: 0;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__intro {
    background: var(--c-science-proof-grid-intro-bg);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 28px 24px;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__subheading {
    color: var(--c-science-proof-grid-cyan);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__heading {
    color: var(--c-science-proof-grid-text);
    font-family: "TT Commons Pro", sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(34px, 8vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    line-height: 1.16;
    margin: 0;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__heading em {
    color: var(--c-science-proof-grid-accent);
    font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__description {
    color: var(--c-science-proof-grid-text);
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__description p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__action-link {
    align-items: center;
    border-bottom: 2px solid currentColor;
    color: var(--c-science-proof-grid-accent);
    display: inline-flex;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    gap: 8px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-top: 4px;
    padding-bottom: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__action-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__action-link[aria-disabled='true'] {
    cursor: default;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__action-icon {
    display: block;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    height: 14px;
    width: 14px;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__drawer-wrap {
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__drawer-wrap .clinical-drawer-trigger {
    align-items: center;
    border-bottom: 2px solid currentColor;
    color: var(--c-science-proof-grid-accent);
    display: inline-flex;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    gap: 8px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-top: 4px;
    padding-bottom: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__drawer-wrap .clinical-drawer-trigger::after {
    content: '\2192';
    display: block;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__drawer-wrap .clinical-drawer-trigger:hover {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__metrics {
    background: var(--c-science-proof-grid-metrics-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-science-proof-grid-metrics-border);
    display: grid;
    gap: 32px;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    padding: 28px 24px;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__metric {
    display: grid;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__metric-header {
    align-items: center;
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__metric-title {
    color: var(--c-science-proof-grid-text);
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__metric-icon-wrap {
    align-items: center;
    display: inline-flex;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    height: 32px;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 32px;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__metric-icon {
    display: block;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    width: 100%;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__metric-icon-placeholder {
    border: 1px solid var(--c-science-proof-grid-accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: block;
    height: 18px;
    width: 18px;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__metric-description {
    color: var(--c-science-proof-grid-text);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 28ch;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__metric-value {
    color: var(--c-science-proof-grid-cyan);
    font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 7vw, 52px);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    line-height: 1.12;
    margin: 0;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__metric-caption {
    color: var(--c-science-proof-grid-caption);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 30ch;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__cta {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__cta-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    background-color: {{ section.settings.cta_bg_color }};
    color: {{ section.settings.cta_text_color }};
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2.1px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
     
  }

  #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__cta-button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    background-color: {{ section.settings.cta_bg_color | color_darken: 10 }};
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__container {
      gap: 30px;
    }

      #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__cta-button {
        font-size: 14px !important;
      }

    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__intro,
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__metrics {
      border-radius: 30px;
      padding: 40px;
    }

    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__metrics {
      gap: 42px 36px;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__metric-title {
      font-size: 24px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 978px) {
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__container {
      align-items: stretch;
      gap: 34px;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 499px) minmax(0, 1fr);
      padding-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom_desktop }}px;
      padding-top: {{ section.settings.padding_top_desktop }}px;
    }

    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__intro {
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 48px;
    }

    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__metrics {
      align-content: center;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      gap: 64px;
      min-height: 100%;
      padding: 64px;
    }

    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__metric-title {
      font-size: 30px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 1200px) {
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__container {
      gap: 61px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 1980px) {
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__container {
      max-width: 1520px;
    }

    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .c-science-proof-grid__heading {
      font-size: 56px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "C Science Proof Grid",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "c-science-proof-grid-wrapper",
  "max_blocks": 8,
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "sl_anchor_id",
      "label": "Anchor ID",
      "info": "HTML anchor for internal navigation"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Background"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "background_image",
      "label": "Background image"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "background_image_alt",
      "label": "Background image alt text",
      "default": "People running outdoors"
    },
    {
      "type": "color",
      "id": "background_overlay_color",
      "label": "Background overlay color",
      "default": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18)"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Column 1 Content"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "subheading",
      "label": "Subheading",
      "default": "The Science"
    },
    {
      "type": "inline_richtext",
      "id": "heading",
      "label": "Heading",
      "default": "One Molecule. <em>Total Health.</em>"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "description",
      "label": "Description",
      "default": "<p>Your body naturally produces Nitric Oxide - the molecule that keeps blood flowing, cells nourished, and your body performing at its best.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "action_link_label",
      "label": "Action link label",
      "default": "See Clinical Trials"
    },
    {
      "type": "url",
      "id": "action_link_url",
      "label": "Action link URL"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "action_link_opens_modal",
      "label": "Open clinical trials modal",
      "default": false
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "action_drawer_title",
      "label": "Action drawer title",
      "default": "Nitric Oxide Support"
